    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I my case I didn't set <code>Source Root</code> at the <code>src</code> folder. I make a typo to set as <code>Resources Root</code>. after fix it by <code>right click at src folder &gt; Mark Directory as &gt; Source Root</code>, the compile error shows.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/u3JKEm.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/u3JKEm.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
